OL,3,C'I left hospital empty-handed
OL,4,Ceveryday': Bed shortage for parents of
OL,5,Csick babies
OL,7,FWords by ITV New Health and Science
OL,8,FProducer Rhiannon Hopley
OL,10,FParents of extremely ill babies are
OL,11,Foften unable to stay in with them due
OL,12,Fto a strained demand on facilities, a
OL,13,Fnew study shows.
OL,15,FFor every 10 babies who require
OL,16,Ftreatment overnight in hospital, there
OL,17,Fis only one room available for a
OL,18,Fparent, according to research by
OL,19,FBliss, a charity for babies born and
OL,20,Fsick.
