OL,3,C'I left hospital empty-handed
OL,4,Ceveryday': Bed shortage for parents of
OL,5,Csick babies
OL,7,FMs Schulz-Apps told ITV News parents
OL,8,Fwould be removed from the rooms if
OL,9,F"someone else who needed it more" came
OL,10,Finto the ward.
OL,12,F"I was walking out of hospital empty
OL,13,Fhanded everyday. It was horrendous,"
OL,14,Fshe said.
OL,16,F"I can't imagine how bad it must be
OL,17,Ffor a nurse to come up to a mum of a
OL,18,Fpremature and sick baby and say your
OL,19,Fbaby isn't poorly enough, you need to
OL,20,Fgo home."
