OL,3,C'I left hospital empty-handed
OL,4,Ceveryday': Bed shortage for parents of
OL,5,Csick babies
OL,7,FOne night, when Ms Schulz-Apps had
OL,8,Fbeen sent home, baby Teddy was taken
OL,9,Fto have a blood transfusion.
OL,11,F"It hits you so hard," she said, "even
OL,12,F15 months on it makes me cry to talk
OL,13,Fabout it."
OL,15,FCaroline Lee-Davey, Chief Executive of
OL,16,FBliss, said Ms Schulz-Apps' story is
OL,17,Fnot unusual. She added: "What our
OL,18,Fresearch has done has put numbers to
OL,19,Fwhat we hear from parents all the time.
