OL,3,C'I left hospital empty-handed
OL,4,Ceveryday': Bed shortage for parents of
OL,5,Csick babies
OL,7,FThis includes updating NHS guidelines,
OL,8,Fnew funding to buy furniture such as
OL,9,Ffold out beds, and a commitment to
OL,10,Fprovide money to allow units to
OL,11,Fconstruct additional space for parents
OL,12,Fto stay.
OL,14,FMs Lee-Davey said giving parents the
OL,15,Fability to stay with their babies is
OL,16,Fcrucial to them and their children.
