OL,3,C'I left hospital empty-handed
OL,4,Ceveryday': Bed shortage for parents of
OL,5,Csick babies
OL,7,F"We know that babies have better
OL,8,Fphysical and developmental outcomes
OL,9,Fwhen their parents are by their side
OL,10,Fas much as possible, and this is
OL,11,Fequally important for parent mental
OL,12,Fhealth and wellbeing, and for parent-
OL,13,Finfant bonding," she added.
OL,15,F"Stopping the separation of parents
OL,16,Ffrom their sick newborns on neonatal
OL,17,Funits is a necessity."
