OL,3,C'I left hospital empty-handed
OL,4,Ceveryday': Bed shortage for parents of
OL,5,Csick babies
OL,7,FA Department of Health and Social Care
OL,8,FSpokesperson said: "We are working
OL,9,Fhard to ensure all maternity services
OL,10,Fprovide safe and compassionate care,
OL,11,Fbut we recognise there's still more
OL,12,Fthat needs to be done.
OL,14,F"That's why we're investing #165
OL,15,Fmillion per year, rising to #186
OL,16,Fmillion from April, to grow the
OL,17,Fmaternity workforce and improve
OL,18,Fmaternity and neonatal care.
